  # QA Report: Demo n8n Email Automation

## 1. Summary
A proof-of-concept subscriber email automation system was built and tested. The system consists of a Node.js/Express backend with a SQLite database storing three demo subscribers, three REST API endpoints, an n8n cloud workflow triggered via webhook, and a simple HTML frontend page. When triggered, the system fetches a subscriber's points balance and details, then sends a personalised email via Mailtrap SMTP sandbox.

## 2. Environment
- **Backend framework:** Node.js with Express
- **Database:** SQLite using better-sqlite3
- **n8n setup:** n8n Cloud free trial (joy6756.app.n8n.cloud)
- **Tunnel:** Cloudflare Tunnel (trycloudflare.com) to expose local backend to n8n
- **Email provider:** Mailtrap sandbox (sandbox.smtp.mailtrap.io, port 2525)
- **Testing tool:** Postman

