## 5. Bugs or Issues Found

| Issue | Expected | Actual | Severity | Suggested Fix |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| Localtunnel URL changes on restart | Stable tunnel URL | New URL generated each restart | Medium | Use Cloudflare Tunnel with fixed subdomain or deploy backend to a hosted service |
| SMTP SSL error with Mailtrap | SMTP connects successfully | SSL handshake error | Medium | Disable STARTTLS in n8n SMTP credential settings |
| n8n webhook test vs production URL | Workflow triggered in production | First calls hit test webhook | Low | Always use production webhook URL and ensure workflow is Published |

