## 7. Final Assessment

**What works:**
- All three API endpoints work correctly with proper error handling
- n8n workflow successfully receives webhook, fetches subscriber data, and sends email
- Email arrives in Mailtrap sandbox with correct subscriber name and points balance
- All 8 Postman tests pass with correct status codes
- Optional frontend page works end to end

**What does not work:**
- Cloudflare tunnel URL changes on every restart requiring n8n node URLs to be updated manually
- Gmail app passwords not available on this Google account

**What should be improved next:**
- Deploy backend to a free hosted service like Railway or Render to avoid tunnel dependency
- Add authentication to the webhook endpoint
- Add email logging to a database table for tracking sent emails
- Add retry logic if n8n webhook fails
